# This file exists to maintain the directory structure in Git.
# The actual binary files (.exe, .dll) should be downloaded separately.
#
# Recommended: download whisper-bin-x64.zip from
# https://github.com/ggml-org/whisper.cpp/releases
# and extract ALL files into this folder (not just whisper-cli.exe).
#
# Required files include:
# - whisper-cli.exe
# - whisper.dll
# - ggml.dll, ggml-base.dll, ggml-cpu.dll
# - SDL2.dll
#
# Optional / deprecated:
# - main.exe (deprecated — use whisper-cli.exe)
